Monday, December 20, 1993

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-1622. Zehman Wolfe Mgt. v. Greenstreet.

Cuyahoga County, No. 65914. This cause is pending before the court on the filing of a motion for an order directing the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County to certify its record. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted.
